dct_title_s: Map of part of central Asia
dct_description_sm: Shows relief by hill shading; Russian provinces; communications.
Compiled from Russian sources and from Col. Walker's map of Turkestan, etc., 1866, revised in 1873 [Second edition of Map of Kirghiz-steppe, etc.].
Coverage: This edn. extends further south.
